<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-46-1295 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Pfirsch-Schlueter classical diffusion of a general stationary toroidalplasma with rational magnetic surfaces and anisotropic pressure is calculated.The effect of pressure anisotropy on the classical diffusion is studied.It is found that the classical diffusion depends on the direction ofthe neutral beam injection.</TEXT></DOC>